📖 Referências Biográficas

Simard, S. (1997). Mycorrhizal networks: Mechanisms, ecology and modelling. Mycorrhiza.

Keeling, P. J., & Palmer, J. D. (2008). Horizontal gene transfer in eukaryotic evolution. Nature Reviews Genetics.

Villarreal, L. P., & Witzany, G. (2010). Viruses are essential agents within the roots and stem of the tree of life. Journal of Theoretical Biology.



